column5: Check the video clip the truck went quite far before stopping.  http://www.theweathernetwork.com/news/storm_watch_stories3&stormfile=trailer_truck_takes_an_icy_p_060112?ref=ccbox_weather_topstories
Crazy. That'll be a big job. Hopefuly the fuel tanks stayed intact.
Yikes.  Hope the driver was OK.
He certainly fell asleep a long ways back ! Bet that woke him up quick!
Wow.  He went right across oncoming traffic, hopefully everyone was okay...
I would say,,,,,,,,,,,,,  He missed his TARGET.  Crazy
Been on that highway a few times. You snooze, you lose.
They are preparing the drivers for when they come to the north!!!!
